  "body": "### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user I want to enable a dark mode setting to make the interface easier on the eyes in dim light conditions, preserve battery on OLED displays, or as a personal preference. \r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nScope of this issue is as follows:\r\n\r\n1. We place an **Appearance** setting in profile\r\n\r\n<img width=\"395\" alt=\"Frame 25\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4932774/76501017-d3f63000-6441-11ea-8f01-9fcb115cb9b2.png\">\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n2. Inside we allow selecting a preference, to **always use Light Mode**, **always use Dark Mode**, or **follow the system setting**.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"395\" alt=\"Group 1\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4932774/76501237-33544000-6442-11ea-9a9f-a59f8f151ed4.png\">\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n3. We add Dark Theme specific colour set that maps to Light, and allow our components to be rendered using either one of them\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1137\" alt=\"Screenshot 2020-03-12 at 09 19 01\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4932774/76501397-84643400-6442-11ea-8b7d-72dca18f31b0.png\">\r\n\r\n<img width=\"860\" alt=\"Group 21\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4932774/76501535-ba091d00-6442-11ea-92f9-98da75a95430.png\">\r\n\r\n<img width=\"884\" alt=\"Group 22\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4932774/76501601-dd33cc80-6442-11ea-8597-77463e9b9b56.png\">\r\n\r\n<img width=\"892\" alt=\"Group 23\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4932774/76501611-e0c75380-6442-11ea-9b6e-ddb21c8950fc.png\">\r\n\r\n<img width=\"800\" alt=\"Group 24\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4932774/76501618-e329ad80-6442-11ea-95fc-ff48c521e5c0.png\">\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\nI'm allowed to select Dark Theme as my appearance preference and see the interface change like so\r\n\r\n![Group 89](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4932774/76501897-63501300-6443-11ea-8406-82af65dce5c8.png)\r\n\r\n<img width=\"800\" alt=\"Group 90\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4932774/76501920-69de8a80-6443-11ea-8416-1f8b1dd0a0d5.png\">\r\n\r\n<img width=\"800\" alt=\"Group 91\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4932774/76501929-6d721180-6443-11ea-95ce-24797453d0c2.png\">\r\n\r\n<img width=\"800\" alt=\"Group 92\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4932774/76501936-7236c580-6443-11ea-99a6-44470bee2628.png\">\r\n\r\n<img width=\"800\" alt=\"Group 93\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4932774/76502003-8da1d080-6443-11ea-8ac9-9b0fc61d349a.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n### Notes\r\n\r\n[Designs in Figma](https://www.figma.com/file/9hkPcxsqDTWa9b9c49OX3X/Dark-Mode?node-id=1%3A85)\r\n\r\nsome of the dark theme colours are subject to change in the next day or two while I do some testing üòé \r\nwhen in need of assistance, holla at maciej.stateofus.eth\r\n\r\nThank you, u r awesome! üôè \r\n",
